$PROB RUN# 104
$INPUT C ID TIME EVID AMT CMT WT DOSE DV
$DATA ../../data/104.csv IGNORE=C
$SUBROUTINES ADVAN2 TRANS2
$PK
TVCL=THETA(1)*(WT/70)**0.75 CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))
TVV2=THETA(2)*(WT/70) V=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2))
TVKA=THETA(3) KA=TVKA*EXP(ETA(3))
$ERROR IPRED=A(2)/(V/1000) Y=IPRED*EXP(ERR(1))
CP = IPRED
REPI = IREP
$THETA (1, FIX) ;; CL (20, FIX) ;; V (1.5, FIX) ;; KA
$OMEGA 0.09 FIX 0.1 FIX 0.2 FIX
$SIGMA 0.025 FIX
$TABLE FILE=TAB REPI ID TIME EVID CP IPRED PRED DV DOSE NOPRINT NOHEADER NOAPPEND
$SIMULATION (2674474) SUBPROBLEM = 1000 ONLYSIMULATION
